Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.03,0:01:47.04,tk-title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(296,227)}來吧！\N松陽祭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.77,0:01:51.73,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨2年D班辦亞洲咖啡廳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.14,0:01:53.74,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,要來佔一卦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.52,0:01:58.35,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨 這邊是恐怖館哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.94,0:02:00.07,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不見了吶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.47,0:02:01.05,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.63,0:02:03.24,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,三位來客
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.77,0:02:08.63,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,給三位 帶路 要注射了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.12,0:02:11.43,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是在幹什麼呀 書獃女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.80,0:02:16.16,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,因道路有雜物 所以請小心腳下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.42,0:02:18.36,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,要注射了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.50,0:02:21.90,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是搞什麼啊 那句 要注射了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.95,0:02:23.94,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你聽到沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.18,0:02:26.30,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,這間廢棄的房子以前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:34.30,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 有目擊此屋主人欲求鮮血而在四處徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:36.43,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(568,62,504,60)\fs50\pos(568,62)\frz353.2\fn方正苏新诗柳楷简体\c&H46225E&\3c&H6E7069&}戀 之 泉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:36.43,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(939,339,889,334)\fs48\fn@方正苏新诗柳楷简体\frz257.3\pos(939,339)\c&H232861&\3c&H526A64&}各種願望都能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.32,0:02:36.57,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 這個護士一點幹勁都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.80,0:02:38.65,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說為什麼裝扮成護士呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.43,0:02:38.94,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(492,92,563,81)\fs50\frz13.45\fn方正少儿_GBK\c&H3F56A0&\3c&H3D323D&\pos(492,92)}胸 部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.25,0:02:43.13,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼大家 慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:45.31,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 很讓人火大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.62,0:02:56.95,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊啊 開玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.98,0:03:02.29,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 春
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.65,0:03:04.35,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都幹了些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.65,0:03:06.28,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:07.44,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的致命武器
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.69,0:03:10.05,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣我們會沒法搭訕了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:12.07,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為補償給我們介紹女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:13.41,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:19.32,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.89,0:03:22.98,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,前段時間因為控制不住情緒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.99,0:03:24.57,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,一瞬間猶豫起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.56,0:03:26.60,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:29.32,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全沒有什麼好慌張的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.33,0:03:31.64,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,由我來改變
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.83,0:03:33.47,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:36.30,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,春他說的太若無其事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.51,0:03:40.61,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是從什麼時候開始 變得這麼容易動搖的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.37,0:03:43.57,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,對自己決定的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.58,0:03:45.10,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從來都沒有迷茫過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.65,0:03:49.86,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為一直以來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.25,0:03:52.42,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我下的決定都是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:57.36,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.47,0:04:01.30,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直像那個時候一樣獨自一人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.53,0:04:04.14,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許也就不會現在這樣亂想了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.05,0:04:09.29,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊 文化祭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:11.03,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 滿善
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:13.50,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底想幹什麼啊 優山
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.47,0:04:17.22,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是已經答應過春 不會再和他相見了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.41,0:04:21.82,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊 那個春竟然為了這個文化祭 都徹夜了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:25.59,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 請給我兩個紅豆甜甜圈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.79,0:04:26.90,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:29.73,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他看見我在這裏出現的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.80,0:04:32.39,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會露出相當討厭的表情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.99,0:04:35.08,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是超級期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:38.38,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要為了這種事讓我陪你來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.72,0:04:40.93,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,開玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:42.46,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知到你說的是真是假啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.21,0:04:49.73,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:50.82,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.57,0:04:53.66,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.93,0:04:56.94,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我嗎？ 我正準備回去 拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:14.45,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏的後院真是寬廣吶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.38,0:05:16.16,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:18.61,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接向誰問下路不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.14,0:05:21.71,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我討厭向他人求助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:22.91,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:24.54,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明都已經迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:27.62,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.75,0:05:32.02,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.25,0:05:33.41,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:41.86,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,山賢君 要一起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.97,0:05:44.66,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不是的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.45,0:05:47.59,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明說好給我們介紹女孩的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.60,0:05:48.71,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼是隻雞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.72,0:05:50.10,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,近來過得好麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:53.76,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 因為我很中意這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.39,0:05:55.87,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說這到底在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.20,0:05:58.52,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這個世上 有很多危險的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.88,0:06:00.43,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了安全起見 所以我做了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.77,0:06:02.36,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字就叫做 水谷雫……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.37,0:06:04.17,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,別把那種東西起名叫 人家的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:07.25,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 山賢你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:09.07,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.60,0:06:11.53,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,在後院迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.54,0:06:12.60,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有迷路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.91,0:06:15.51,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,春 佐佐原叫我們回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.71,0:06:18.17,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼雫會和山賢在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.18,0:06:20.03,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰……碰巧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.93,0:06:22.63,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要避開我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:24.31,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂喂 春
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.43,0:06:26.38,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼能這樣逼迫女孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.42,0:06:27.61,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,太不像樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.05,0:06:30.45,tk-default2,NTP,0,0,0,,我們輪流拍照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.63,0:06:32.19,tk-default2,NTP,0,0,0,,下一個是我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:28.26,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.12,0:06:31.18,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等等 雫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:33.72,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不讓我沒有允許的就碰觸你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.73,0:06:35.37,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻讓這個傢伙隨便碰你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:36.05,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.05,0:06:36.94,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我並有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.32,0:06:38.37,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是擺明了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.72,0:06:41.84,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以碰 但你不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.30,0:06:44.91,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我離開雫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.52,0:06:53.37,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇哇啊 直接擊中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:53.99,tk-default2,NTP,0,0,0,,打到臉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:55.58,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對不起 雫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.67,0:06:56.23,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是事故
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:57.57,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕快道歉 春
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.57,0:06:59.37,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕快好好道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.92,0:06:58.80,tk-default2,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在做什麼呢 無腦男
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.40,0:07:01.84,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到底 還不是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.84,0:07:03.39,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？竟然要把錯推到我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:05.54,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,春
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.54,0:07:06.13,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.41,0:07:09.51,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,以後絕對不允許……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:13.14,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,進入我半徑兩米之內
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.06,0:07:21.54,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,小水 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:22.96,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.16,0:07:24.76,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在生氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:26.26,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:28.02,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我並沒有生氣、
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.87,0:07:29.55,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.11,0:07:33.40,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣被春耍的團團轉的自己真有點傻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.31,0:07:38.24,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,他那樣 和不辨是非的小孩沒區別
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.84,0:07:41.04,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,傲慢而且只考慮自己的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:42.51,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.04,0:07:46.30,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我還是無法丟下他不管
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:50.08,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,這……這難道是 戀愛咨詢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.89,0:07:53.29,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:55.46,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,男女間的愛情是剪不斷理還亂的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.47,0:07:57.96,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,正所謂Best Of Only One啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.49,0:08:01.15,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,春選擇和我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.28,0:08:03.59,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是因為他不想孤單一人罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.72,0:08:04.56,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:07.87,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對他來說…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.16,0:08:10.73,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不過是正好出現在他身邊的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:16.73,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,小水 你不相信春同學嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:20.62,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰都不想孤單一人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.88,0:08:22.83,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,理所當然會認為待在自己身旁的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:25.48,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,對自己來說是特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:30.50,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,小水 難道你對春沒有這種感覺嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.36,0:08:35.17,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.14,0:08:37.17,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 夏目同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:40.98,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,這件事和你無關
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.87,0:08:51.11,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是好冷淡啊 那個書獃女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.31,0:08:55.45,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 還不是因為山賢亂插手春的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:57.93,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？關我什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:00.57,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 去嗎？去安慰她嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:02.71,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 還是在這多觀察一會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:11.03,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,小水你不相信春嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.66,0:09:14.88,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼事情會變成這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.59,0:09:17.94,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.08,0:09:21.62,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的鼻子因為我被打成那樣 我也很不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.73,0:09:24.82,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,追究起來確實是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.88,0:09:26.96,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 真可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.22,0:09:29.97,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,被你討厭了的話 春又要變成孤單一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.81,0:09:31.54,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,又？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.72,0:09:36.23,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來告訴你吧 為什麼你無法丟下那傢伙不管
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.99,0:09:37.84,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你聽到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:39.66,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你對他有所期待
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.11,0:09:43.75,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,對方的言行中也混有你的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.26,0:09:46.22,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你才會放不下春
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:48.95,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己任性的期待著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.27,0:09:51.29,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是卻無法回應對方的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:53.46,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是個殘酷的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:54.82,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,水谷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.82,0:09:58.49,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(944,526,952,227)\fad(0,700)\fs50\fn方正粗活意简体\c&H2E1EB9&\3c&HF6DC81&\pos(944,526)}刨\N\N冰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:01.59,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不和我保持距離的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:03.05,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我無法和你做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.44,0:10:06.13,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,這件事和你無關
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.48,0:10:11.06,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不是傷害到他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:15.52,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼？難道是現在一個人覺得寂寞了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:18.17,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不巧 一直以來我都是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:20.48,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,從沒有覺得寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.13,0:10:22.14,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨~蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:23.91,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,寂寞這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.92,0:10:25.98,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要有朋友之後才會感覺到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:30.18,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:33.48,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.37,0:10:40.00,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:43.92,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,優山先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:44.97,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也來…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.85,0:10:49.97,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？優山
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.41,0:10:52.92,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不… 什麼事都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.44,0:11:03.51,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,…痛痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.86,0:11:06.91,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡！為什麼那傢伙會在這裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.88,0:11:09.60,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你認識優山先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.83,0:11:11.07,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為他們兄弟倆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.08,0:11:13.02,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前都在海明高中上學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:16.21,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你害怕優山先生嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.49,0:11:19.84,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 怎麼會有我害怕的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.90,0:11:23.47,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是…有點心理陰影
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:25.95,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得你的自尊心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:27.64,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天會毀了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.80,0:11:28.60,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,要你管
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.95,0:11:32.09,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,山賢同學 請讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.10,0:11:35.18,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,事先說明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.62,0:11:37.36,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對你可是一點都沒有慾念哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:39.76,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？你在說什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.02,0:11:41.69,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,快躲起來！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.52,0:11:43.89,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒…誒？ 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.90,0:11:44.57,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.23,0:11:46.56,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 是女生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.24,0:11:48.70,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:50.40,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉…吉田同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:08.88,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡！那個鰻魚混蛋竟然敢違背約定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:12.50,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？什麼？之前說過的那個鰻魚人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.51,0:12:13.58,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,是指剛才那個人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.38,0:12:17.63,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 今天到底怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:19.80,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,大島
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.88,0:12:23.14,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我說喜歡你的話 你會覺得討厭嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.94,0:12:26.70,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？誒？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.70,0:12:28.85,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我我該怎麼回答？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:31.13,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我覺得越是和雫說我喜歡她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.29,0:12:34.71,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,狀況就會變得越來越糟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.32,0:12:37.49,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話 就只好霸王硬上弓了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:39.23,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.70,0:12:42.33,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說這件事啊 誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:46.99,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這麼一回事啊 作為當事人你也解釋下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.76,0:12:48.66,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,無可奉告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:56.21,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那麼 如果我說我喜歡吉田同學的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.98,0:12:58.76,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同學會怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.94,0:13:03.43,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什麼啊 這麼平白無故的問我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:05.72,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不討厭你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:09.06,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.32,0:13:11.76,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 不是指這個意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:15.54,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…那個 怎麼說好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.33,0:13:18.91,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是雌性追求喜歡的雄性的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:24.05,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種…那種是要做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.76,0:13:27.73,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是的 我不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.75,0:13:27.60,tk-default2,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 偷聽別人說話不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:28.89,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.26,0:13:30.87,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在正是精彩的時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.87,0:13:31.60,tk-default2,NTP,0,0,0,,更像柏拉圖式的那種…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.87,0:13:31.57,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:35.58,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 春
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.90,0:13:41.02,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們倆為什麼會在這種地方！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:47.92,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.35,0:13:50.60,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,和小雫說了比較深入的意見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.71,0:13:52.78,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果被她斷然拒之門外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:55.13,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,春和我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:13:57.75,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不過是因為不想孤單一人罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.91,0:14:02.97,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直就像我的心事 被看穿了似的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.05,0:14:07.30,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不小心就對小水說了責備她的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:10.87,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得小水第一次 和我說這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.06,0:14:15.04,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 小夏目確實是生氣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.26,0:14:17.21,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家相互把火發出來就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:21.32,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們女孩子一旦吵架了 就全都結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.82,0:14:24.49,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是給夏目朝子最後通牒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.96,0:14:28.48,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是結束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.07,0:14:32.40,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,主要取決於 你自己是否還想和她做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.91,0:14:34.31,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼好怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.94,0:14:38.62,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這是我的第一個朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:40.30,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想失去她！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.39,0:14:42.88,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈 就是這種幹勁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:44.20,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起！了不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.25,0:14:46.24,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不想主動和她道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:45.54,tk-default2,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 找到了！找到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.38,0:14:47.82,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏目同學你在做什…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.71,0:14:48.43,tk-default2,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到你脾氣這麼倔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.56,0:14:51.01,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼在哭？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.44,0:14:53.99,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 有很多原因啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:56.06,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 棒球少年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.27,0:14:57.60,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,店長 你來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.95,0:14:58.81,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人來的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.88,0:15:00.74,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…和優山一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.18,0:15:02.53,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正好該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:11.23,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你瞧 春
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.75,0:15:13.59,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,觀眾都聚過來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.74,0:15:15.31,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,切…囉嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:16.39,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,別過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.67,0:15:18.76,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又打算鬧事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:33.36,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,春
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.04,0:15:37.01,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子真的怎麼樣都無所謂嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:44.50,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,春！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.29,0:15:50.29,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊啊 真可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.79,0:15:58.09,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,大島同學 沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:16:00.21,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.96,0:16:04.66,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起呢 我弟弟給你添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.84,0:16:06.53,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.97,0:16:10.40,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,來得正好 我有事找小雫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.52,0:16:15.87,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 我正麻煩她帶路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:21.01,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還想是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.02,0:16:22.94,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,該不會是山口先生家的賢二吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.14,0:16:24.78,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你長大了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:27.54,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雫 這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.53,0:16:31.33,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛春逃跑時落下的鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.62,0:16:32.66,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫我還給他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.91,0:16:33.91,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:35.55,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我送你回教室
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.73,0:16:37.19,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.23,0:16:39.07,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,收好 你的生意道具
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.13,0:16:40.86,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.97,0:16:42.99,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,再會嘍 小雫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:48.05,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 在這呢在這呢 讓我好找
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.06,0:16:50.32,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在這和書獃女做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:51.69,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.73,0:16:52.67,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.21,0:16:54.82,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見啦 水谷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.83,0:16:58.67,tk-default2,NTP,0,0,0,,好可疑×N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:56.27,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.22,0:17:01.15,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:15.20,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然這麼鬱悶的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:17.28,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,就想清楚後再行動怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.29,0:17:19.90,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:21.71,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.20,0:17:24.61,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 反省一下比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.09,0:17:26.26,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:31.54,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我也一樣是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:35.23,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,總是搞錯事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:40.48,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道不要兩米了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.86,0:17:44.71,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 那個可以取消了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:48.03,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我發現訂規則也是沒意義的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.11,0:17:50.67,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你終於明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:51.79,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:08.10,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 我先去跟大島道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.43,0:18:09.00,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.62,0:18:14.84,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要發現錯誤 想要改正並不是難事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.45,0:18:16.25,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:18.64,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.27,0:18:22.35,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏目好心給我意見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.55,0:18:25.47,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的態度太沒有誠意了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:28.83,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,這件事我想跟你說對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:37.05,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我是小水和春同學的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.73,0:18:39.74,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,並不是沒有關係的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.40,0:18:42.18,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.29,0:18:44.96,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏目同學說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:00.39,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.77,0:19:02.44,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 總算找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:05.90,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們也差不多工作了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.14,0:19:07.25,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:36.20,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,春 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.85,0:19:39.78,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:56.94,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 原來是雫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.28,0:19:58.71,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,別嚇我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.87,0:20:00.42,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我要說的話！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:02.15,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你剛才想做什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.18,0:20:03.01,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.41,0:20:08.25,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我想摸摸你的頭髮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.26,0:20:10.44,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 頭髮？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.68,0:20:18.76,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,雫的想法我實在不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.76,0:20:21.14,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴上說沒事看起來卻相反
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.14,0:20:23.42,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然又說不讓我靠近你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.34,0:20:27.48,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,進也不是退也不是 到底要我怎樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.61,0:20:30.02,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這麼問我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.51,0:20:39.26,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 春無論何時都是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.15,0:20:41.55,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,手好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:47.28,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直不去正面面對的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.21,0:20:52.50,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,被你這麼逼問 我也有想過的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.98,0:20:55.03,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會是這種心情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:20:57.94,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的選擇正確嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.81,0:21:00.39,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是我搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:06.73,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我會不會又喜歡你到 無法專心唸書
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.40,0:21:12.85,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 最後還是在學習中平靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.90,0:21:14.54,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦！嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.69,0:21:17.16,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來我一直是和學習戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.67,0:21:23.33,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要這樣 不想再有那種感受了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.38,0:21:26.40,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想變得不能好好讀書
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.74,0:21:29.74,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,雫?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.66,0:21:32.92,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是不唸書我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.57,0:21:39.31,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你突然幹什麼春！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.32,0:21:40.69,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.83,0:21:42.09,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪裏知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.09,0:21:44.97,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.42,0:21:46.79,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,心臟…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.66,0:21:48.66,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.34,0:21:51.29,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像之前曾經這樣過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.03,0:21:55.93,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.73,0:21:58.84,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候我感覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.52,0:22:02.11,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,身邊真實的體溫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.87,0:22:06.26,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人感到舒服 卻有點悲傷的安心感
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.24,0:22:09.54,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一天的我所不知道的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.45,0:22:13.06,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,春
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.21,0:22:13.87,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.29,0:22:18.22,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能再給我點時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.91,0:22:21.53,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會好好考慮春的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.25,0:22:24.18,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,學會面對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.18,0:22:26.05,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不論我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.55,0:22:27.36,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有春
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.13,0:22:31.46,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都是從這裏開始
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.02,0:24:22.02,next title1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.71,0:22:47.80,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,星の街路中　君と歩き町
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.37,0:22:54.97,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,笑った途端白い息が凍えそう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.04,0:23:02.06,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,あ　どうして今日も冗談ばかりで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.06,0:23:09.69,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,相変わらず微妙な距離もどかしくて切ないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.76,0:23:19.62,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,巡る巡る冬の夜は今年は　あ　高いね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.93,0:23:26.13,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,味方だって　寂さだって　何だか嬉しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.19,0:23:33.55,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,「今日が回りしよう」君から言わないかな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.00,0:23:41.01,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,これが恋か恋じゃないかどっちだって構わない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.21,0:23:47.40,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,不器用でも喧嘩してもやっぱり君がいい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.40,0:23:54.70,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,降り出した雪に願いをかけるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.45,0:24:03.10,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,あとちょっとこのままで二人きり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.71,0:22:47.80,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,繁星點點的街道上 與你漫步而行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.37,0:22:54.97,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,歡笑間呵出的白色霧氣似乎一瞬就會被冰凍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.04,0:23:02.06,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 今天你也總是說些玩笑話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.06,0:23:09.69,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,我們之間的微妙距離依然如此讓人焦躁苦悶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.76,0:23:19.62,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,斗轉星移今年的冬季 夜晚的天空很高呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.93,0:23:26.13,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,因為有知己 就算會寂寞 仍有些莫名的開心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.19,0:23:33.55,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,「今天去哪裏轉轉吧」你會不會說出這樣的話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.00,0:23:41.01,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,無論這是否是戀愛都沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.21,0:23:47.40,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,就算很笨拙就算會吵架只要有你在就好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.40,0:23:54.70,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,向飄落的雪花許下心願
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.45,0:24:03.10,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,就像這樣繼續在二人世界多停留一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.96,0:24:10.14,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明那麼可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.24,0:24:11.96,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近卻很冷淡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.19,0:24:13.87,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,是說血緣是不能違背的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.07,0:24:15.79,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說想違背也無濟於事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.62,0:24:20.09,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我漸漸深以為然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.30,0:24:21.85,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
